<i>adverb</i>: 연거푸 [연거푸], 속속 [속쏙], 내리 [내리], 계속 [계ː속/게ː속], 거푸 [거푸] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>연거푸 [연거푸]</dt><br>
<dd>successively; in succession; repeatedly</dd><br>
<dd>여러 번 계속해서.</dd><br>
<dd>Several times in a row.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>속속 [속쏙]</dt><br>
<dd>one after another; successively; one upon the heels of another</dd><br>
<dd>이어서 계속.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuously in succession.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>내리 [내리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. successively; at a stretch; in a row</dd><br>
<dd>잇달아 계속해서.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuously one after another.</dd><br>
<dd>2. severely; wildly</dd><br>
<dd>사정없이 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>Violently without mercy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>계속 [계ː속/게ː속]</dt><br>
<dd>1. continuously; successively</dd><br>
<dd>끊이지 않고 잇따라.</dd><br>
<dd>Continually without interruption.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in the manner of resuming</dd><br>
<dd>중단됐던 일을 다시 이어서.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of beginning something again after interruption.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거푸 [거푸]</dt><br>
<dd>successively</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 거듭하여.</dd><br>
<dd>One after another.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>